“Putting yourself first is not selfish it is necessary” I can’t believe it’s going to be a year since I changed my life for the better. This year I really choose myself and didn’t feel bad about it. Looking at these before pictures are so hard because I never want to go back to that place of feeling unwanted. I’ve never felt more confident and sexy in my body now. I made a pack that before I turn 30 I was going to feel the best I’ve ever felt. I’m happy, I’m having fun, I finally feel like myself. Cheers to 2023 because it’s time to get back to the grind and have even more fun. Can’t wait to show you what’s in store! ✨
